# ============================================================
#  MIT Virtual Park — Daily.co Video Room Configuration
# ============================================================
#
# HOW TO SET UP (takes ~5 minutes):
#
#  1. Sign up at https://dashboard.daily.co  (free tier: 10 participants / 1000 min/month)
#  2. Copy your "Subdomain" from the Dashboard settings page
#     → Set VITE_DAILY_DOMAIN below (e.g. "my-school" → rooms at my-school.daily.co)
#  3. Go to "Developers" → copy your API key
#     → Set VITE_DAILY_API_KEY below
#  4. Copy this file to ".env.local" (git-ignored) and fill in your values:
#
#       cp .env.example .env.local
#
#  5. Run "npm run dev" — the app will auto-create Daily rooms named after
#     each PARK-XXXX room code and participants can join with the invite link.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY NOTE: API keys starting with VITE_ are embedded in the client
#     bundle and visible in source. This is acceptable for a class demo/MVP.
#     For production, move room creation to a backend server.
# ============================================================

VITE_DAILY_DOMAIN=your-subdomain
VITE_DAILY_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
